  <a href="#1" id="1">
   Japan's Emperor Hirohito, posthumously named Showa,
  </a>
  <a href="#2" id="2">
   left a $13 million taxable estate.
  </a>
  <a href="#3" id="3">
   He died of cancer on Jan. 7.
  </a>
